{
  "stem": "16792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 372.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was his eyes in time when I was in Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we was going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I couldn't go very fast, but we was going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we came to a certain part after-- after, I think, a couple weeks, running every day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "What we ate is I picked up from the fields, I picked up carrots, and I picked up potatoes, and we make some fire to-- on the outside.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We was-- we was running, and this is the way we ate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We didn't see bread a long time because we didn't pass any city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We only pass to the way to go straight how fast we can-- we can go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we came to a certain place, and my grandfather told me that he couldn't run too fast, that I should go away alone.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because he said that the German, when they-- when they take people from 17, 18 years old, they kill them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That's what he said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I don't want to go, but my grandfather said to go, I go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I say goodbye to my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I kiss everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And my grandfather put a hand on my head, and he [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I didn't took with me nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I've got a little bit of money with me, zloties.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I left it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I don't need nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I left, and when I was running, and I run faster, I met a friend from our city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And his name-- I don't know he still lives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I hope he's still alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Leon Klappholtz is his name, Leon Klappholtz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We calling him [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Lipe ?] Klappholtz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And-- and we got together, and we run together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we run very, very, very fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
